{"tid":1031132,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本旅行咩地方少大陸人","createTime":"2019-02-21T12:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T06:34:22.000Z","uid":133743,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"e4848bc8ab83cafd9d3c510efd6ab931767a8bc1","tid":1031132,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:24:18.000Z","msg":"呢兩三年去日本連D所謂秘景都有大陸人，仲有咩地方推薦唔使聽到普通話？<br />\n前兩年去彥根聽唔到普通話，反而好多鬼佬。<br />\n彥根貓好頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F78xNJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF78xNJ3.png&h=7d1bf2ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ddfe0694a72946414fcdc28c2f5df55ca687e13","tid":1031132,"uid":60635,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"無得鳩鳴既地方就少大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n之前去札幌雪祭無乜點聽到普通話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為一街講廣東話既仲嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df550ece2b98322a2057dad9aab263c1a559b7eb","tid":1031132,"uid":133743,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7ddfe0694a72946414fcdc28c2f5df55ca687e13","tid":1031132,"uid":60635,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:31:37.000Z","msg":"無得鳩鳴既地方就少大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n之前去札幌雪祭無乜點聽到普通話。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為一街講廣東話既仲嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"小樽就成個大陸咁淨係聽到普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728d9e3558037b7b1cc808898bc7045080fc